{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"language","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sending notifications in a specific language","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Language-based segmentation","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Supporting in-app language switching"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Support in-app language selection:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)","type":"text"}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"title":"setLanguage:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collect